text: A very sweet family business, with good coffee and tea on a warm day. To go in, just walk right into the clubhouse Incredibly chatty and good space to relax on your off day. The food is simple but a hearty meal. Support them if you can!
The fried rice and chicken chop tasted delicious! Will definitely come back!
Family business with a good home cooked meal. The aunty is so kind and give us cookies.
Delicious chicken chop, especially loved the sauce !
